OOC: Ah, gotcha.

DarkMouse::
She saw the signatures of the bots returning to base.  She shrugged 
her shoulders. "I wish I was out there fighting. After all, I'm tough 
enough. I took on Megatron and won. I saw the matrix and came back. 
Dang I wish I wasn't that good with computer systems. I'd be fighting 
and not stuck behind a desk all the time." she griped to herself 
under her breath. 
She turned and faced KitKat2 and Drillbit. "Would you guys go and get 
a room. Your makng me sick with all that kissing and mush. I'm sorry 
boss, but it's making me ill." she said with a grimice on her face.  

She shook her head,"Some bots, I swear." turned and faced her 
computer screen.
